        {
          question: 'Which browsers is Kairy compatible with?',
          answer: 'Kairy is currently compatible with Google Chrome and Mozilla Firefox.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Can I use Kairy on multiple devices?',
          answer:
            'Yes, you can use Kairy on multiple devices by signing up for an account. This will allow you to sync your bookmarks, reading lists, and tasks across all your devices.',
        },
      ],
      [
        {
          question: 'Is my data secure with Kairy?',
          answer:
            'Yes, all data saved in Kairy is stored locally on your device and is not sent anywhere. Kairy also does not use any tracking code or cookies.',
        },
        {
          question: 'How can I organize my bookmarks and reading lists in Kairy?',
          answer:
            'You can organize your bookmarks and reading lists in Kairy by creating categories and tags. This allows you to easily manage and find specific bookmarks.',
        },
        {
          question: 'How do I create a bookmark in Kairy?',
